\sin \left(6a\right)=-\frac{\sqrt{5}}{3}\:::::::\cos \left(6a\right)>0\:::::::::Find:\:\sin \left(3a\right)\:and\:\tan \left(12a\right)
\sin \left(\frac{1}{2}a\right)=-\frac{2}{3}
\sin 6a=-\sqrt5/3
\cos 6a>0
\cos 2x=1-2\sin^2x
\sin x=\pm\sqrt{\frac{1-\cos 2x}2}
6a
 \cos 6a=\sqrt{1-(-\sqrt5/3)^2}=\sqrt{1-5/9}=\frac23 
 \sin 3a=\sqrt{\frac{1-\cos6a}2}=\sqrt{\frac{1-2/3}2}=\frac1{\sqrt6}. 
 \tan 12a=\frac{\sin 12a}{\cos12a}=\frac{2\sin6a\cos6a}{1-\sin^26a}=2\,\frac{-\sqrt5/3\times2/3}{1-2\times5/9}=4\sqrt5. 
